  "title": "Service Engineer (Up to $3000 / 5 days / Jurong)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title : Service Engineer (ID3569)<br />Location : Jurong<br />Working Hours: Mon -Fri 8:30am-5:30pm<br />Salary up to : $2500-$3000<br /><br />Job Descriptions :<br />• Attend site commissioning with customers and contractors.<br />• Conduct end-user training for Intruder Alarm, CCTV, and Access Control systems.<br />• Inspect and verify installations to ensure compliance with technical and quality requirements.<br />• Confirm systems meet quotation/work order specifications and prepare commissioning reports.<br />• Respond to service calls, troubleshoot, and repair system issues on-site.<br />• Diagnose and test faulty equipment and provide technical support to customers.<br />• Coordinate with internal teams and suppliers for parts replacement or escalation.<br />• Ensure high customer satisfaction through timely and professional service.<br /><br />Job Requirements:<br />• Diploma or NITEC in Electrical / Electronic / Mechatronic Engineering or related field.<br />• Experience in Intruder Alarm, CCTV and Access control systems or similar low-voltage systems preferred.Good communication and customer service skills.<br />• Strong troubleshooting, problem-solving, and technical skills.<br />• Independent, responsible, and able to work under minimal supervision.</p>",
